resentation to describing the\nnon-relativistic Aharonov-Bohm paradox is presented. The current algebra\ncoherent functional representations are constructed and their importance\nsubject to the linearization problem of nonlinear dynamical systems in Hilbert\nspaces is demonstrated.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 16 Apr 2012 05:28:53 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 2 Feb 2013 00:00:27 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 16 Feb 2013 11:19:03 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Tue, 2 Apr 2013 20:44:50 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Sat, 31 Oct 2015 23:47:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-11-03"}
